<title><![CDATA[Chicken, Pumpkin and Olives Tajine]]></title>
<description><![CDATA[If you have never cooked with whole spices before, this is a great recipe to begin. The difference will persuade you to bin those dusty pre-ground spices forever. A small mortar and pestle is all you need to get started.]]></description>
